an="2"><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0">&nbsp;</p></td></tr><tr><td width="20%" valign="top" align="left"><b><font size="2" face="Tahoma">Description:</font></b></td><td width="80%" valign="top" align="left"><font size="2" face="Tahoma"><b>1. </b>Talk to Sern Adolia, who lives in Paineel, and he will tell you he is trying to summon the Avatar of Fright! He requires special components for the ritual and wants you to retrieve them for him.
<br><br>
<b>2. </b>Flesh of a Zombie can be found off a Zombie all over but I went to Befallen lots of undead there.
<br><br>
<b>3. </b>The next item you need is the Embalming Dust, which can be found off Mummies all over but again I went to Befallen.
<br><br>
<b>4. </b>To locate the Charred Bone Chips, kill Obretl a named Flaming Skeleton which can be found in South Ro.
<br><br>
<b>5. </b>Finally, to obtain the Vial of Tunare's Breath, head to Lesser Faydark and find a Druid named Kalayia.
<br><br>
<b>6. </b>Bring Sern back all these ingredients and you will receive the Forged Fright Helm!  Awesome effect for a cleric!</font></td></tr><tr><td width="100%" valign="top" align="left" colspan="2"><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0">&nbsp;</p></td></tr><tr><td width="20%" valign="top" align="left"><b><font size="2" face="Tahoma">Author:</font></b></td><td width="80%" valign="top" align="left"><font size="2" face="Tahoma">Bridget (Rallos Zek)</font></td></tr><tr><td width="100%" valign="top" align="left" colspan="2"><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0">&nbsp;</p></td></tr><tr><td width="20%" valign="top" align="left"><b><font size="2" face="Tahoma">Quest Reward:</font></b></td><td width="80%" valign="top" align="left"><font size="2" face="Tahoma"><b>Fright Forged Helm</b></font></td></tr><tr><td width="20%" valign="top" align="left"><b><font size="2" face="Tahoma"></font></b></td><td width="80%" valign="top" align="left"><font size="2" face="Tahoma"><b>Magic Item, Lore Item, NoDrop  AC+11  CHA-5, STR+5, WIS+4, Effect: Deadeye</b></font></td></tr><tr><td width="100%" valign="top" align="left" colspan="2"><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0">&nbsp;</p></td></tr><tr><td width="20%" valign="top" align="left"><b><font size="2" face="Tahoma">Rating:</font></b></td><td width="80%" valign="top" align="left"><font size="2" face="Tahoma"><b>5.8</b> (average of <b>4</b> votes)</font></td></tr><tr><td width="100%" valign="top" align="left" colspan="2"><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0">&nbsp;</p></td></tr><tr><td width="20%" valign="top" align="left" valign="middle"><b><font size="2" face="Tahoma">Rate this quest:</font></b></td><td width="80%" valign="top" align="left" valign="middle"><font size="2" face="Tahoma"><FORM ACTION = "ratequest.asp" METHOD = post><SELECT NAME="Voting"><OPTION VALUE="0">Rate this Quest</OPTION><OPTION VALU